@startuml component
title Pig Game — Component Architecture

skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam shadowing false

actor Player

package "src/" {
  [main.js\n(entry)] as main
  [PigGame\n(pure state machine)] as game
  [ui.js\n(DOM bindings + render)] as ui
}

cloud "DOM\n(#app)" as dom

Player --> dom : click Roll / Hold / New game / target input
dom --> ui : event handlers
ui --> game : roll() / hold() / reset() / setTarget()
game --> ui : subscribe(snapshot)
ui --> dom : update scores, current, active/winner classes, dice img

main --> game : new PigGame()
main --> ui : mount(root, game)

note right of game
  Rules:
  - dice=1 → roundScore=0, turn passes
  - dice=6 after another 6 → total wiped, turn passes
  - hold → roundScore added to total, win if >= target
  - target clamped to [10..1000]
end note
@enduml
